@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Main";
    ViewData["Page"] = "main";
}

<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<div class="hero">
    <div class="banner">
        <div class="banner-header">
            <p class="banner-title">What is FinSys</p>
            <p class="banner-para">A Financial Management System (FMS) made for streamlining financial performance of business</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="banner-button">
            <button class="primary-btn"><a href="#aboutUs">Learn more about FinSys</a></button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="carousel-bottom">
        <div class="carousel-bottom-con">
            <div class="carousel-bottom-header">
                <p class="carousel-para-over">Over 6.9 million subscribers using FinSys</p>
                <p class="carousel-para-awards">Awards and recognition for our work</p>
            </div>

            <div class="carousel-sticker">
                <img src="~/img/Capterra-2025.svg">
                <img src="~/img/software-advice.svg">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="main-subsection">
    <!-- ABOUT US -->
    <div class="about main-subsection-item" id="aboutUs">
        <div class="about-para about-con-item">
            <div class="about-title">
                <p class="about-get">Get To Know Us</p>
                <p class="about-who">Who we are?</p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-desc">
                <p>Finance System or commonly know as FinSys started in 2020, 
                    when a group of researchers in Cavite, Philippines saw the 
                    potential to revolutionize business finance operation through 
                    Software-as-a-service (SaaS). An idea to create a Financial 
                    Management System (FMS) as a service for personal and 
                    businesses, integrating technology for reliable, optimize, and 
                    secured financial operations. The idea that created FinSys, a new 
                    and innovated software that transformed financial operations with 
                    the integration of technology.
                </p>
                <p>
                    FinSys is a Finance Management System that aims to handle the 
                    financial sector of a business. With the aim to streamline financial 
                    operation by centralizing financial data into a single hub optimizing 
                    core processes.
                </p>
            </div> 
        </div>

        <div class="about-img-con about-con-item">
            <div class="about-img">
                <img src="~/img/organizationalChart.svg">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SOLUTION -->
    <div class="solution main-subsection-item" id="solutions">
        <div class="solution-title">
            <p class="solution-finsys-text ">The FinSys Solution</p>
            <p class="solution-whatWeDo-text">What we do?</p>
        </div>

        <div class="solution-container">
            <div class="solution-subtitle">
                <div class="solution-con-item">
                    <p class="solution-subtitle-innovative">Innovative Solutions for Financial Operations</p>
                </div>
                <div class="solution-con-item">
                    <p class="solution-subtitle-explore">Explore FinSys an FMS for managing your everyday finance, it provides financial tool for personal and business use.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cardview">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-img">
                        <img src="~/icons/coins.svg">
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-title">Accounting and Finance</p>
                    <p>FinSys provides tools for managing finance
                        operations such as calculating the income,
                        expenses, and total revenue. With real-time
                        visibility, client can make more informed 
                        and fast decisions leading to more profit and 
                        growth.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card card-con-item">
                    <div class="card-img transaction-icon">
